  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A full 13-factor credibility assessment is performed with Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification. The model was revised in early 2026 to incorporate updated impeller geometry tolerances and revised blood viscosity correlations; however, the primary experimental hemolysis dataset used to anchor model inputs retains a dataVintage of 2025-10-15, predating the modelRevisionDate of 2026-02-01. Re-validation against post-revision experimental data is noted as planned but not yet executed.",
