      "name": "FDA Generic Centrifugal Pump Hemolysis Experimental Dataset (2025 Q4)",
      "description": "In-vitro hemolysis measurements for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump across five flow-speed operating points. Data collected under ISO 10993-4 protocols using porcine blood. This dataset was finalized on 2025-10-15 and serves as the primary experimental anchor for model input calibration and validation. Re-validation against post-revision experimental data is planned following the 2026-02-01 model revision but has not yet been completed.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-10-15T00:00:00Z",
      "source": "https://doi.org/10.17632/fda-centrifugal-pump-hemolysis-2025"
    },
